            "title": "Hidden diversity of Nycteribiidae (Diptera) bat flies from the Malagasy region and insights on host-parasite interactions",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Beza",
                    "lastName": "Ramasindrazana"
                },
                {
