            "title": "Habitat aridity as a determinant of the trade-off between water conservation and evaporative heat loss in bats",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Agustí",
                    "lastName": "Muñoz-Garcia"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
